1
00:00:08,625 --> 00:00:11,208
- MY NAME'S NINA AND I'M A
PRETTY AVERAGE, ORDINARY GIRL.

2
00:00:11,291 --> 00:00:14,000
AT LEAST I WAS,
UNTIL ONE DAY.

3
00:00:14,083 --> 00:00:16,166
I ACCIDENTALLY SWALLOWED
SOMETHING CALLED

4
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:18,541
THE CRYSTAL PEARL WHILE EATING
AT MY FAVORITE CAKE SHOP,

5
00:00:18,625 --> 00:00:20,958
AND MY LIFE
HASN'T BEEN THE SAME EVER SINCE.

6
00:00:21,041 --> 00:00:24,625
THIS PEARL IS AN IMPORTANT PART
OF AN OTHERWORLDLY SORCERY TEST.

7
00:00:24,708 --> 00:00:26,750
IT'S DROPPED RANDOMLY
INTO THE HUMAN WORLD,

8
00:00:26,833 --> 00:00:28,500
AND THE TEAM OF TWO EXAMINEES
WHO ARE ABLE

9
00:00:28,583 --> 00:00:30,666
TO TRACK IT DOWN FIRST
WILL PASS THE EXAMINATION

10
00:00:30,750 --> 00:00:32,958
AND BECOME
PROFESSIONAL SORCERERS.

11
00:00:33,041 --> 00:00:36,500
THEN GET THIS THING OUT OF ME!
- STOP CRYING.

12
00:00:36,583 --> 00:00:38,500
- YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO PREPARE YOURSELF, ZERO.

13
00:00:38,583 --> 00:00:39,625
- HUH?

14
00:00:39,708 --> 00:00:40,958
- NOW THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY
TO DO THIS.

15
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:42,958
LOOKS LIKE WE'LL HAVE TO
PROTECT HER ANY WAY WE CAN

16
00:00:43,041 --> 00:00:45,083
UNTIL THE DAY THE TEST IS OVER.

17
00:00:45,166 --> 00:00:47,166
WE'LL KEEP DILIGENT WATCH OVER
HER UNTIL THE MEDICINE IS READY

18
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:49,375
AND WE CAN EXTRACT
THE CRYSTAL PEARL FROM HER BODY.

19
00:00:49,458 --> 00:00:51,583
WE'LL HAVE TO PROTECT THIS GIRL
WITH OUR VERY LIVES.

20
00:00:51,666 --> 00:00:53,166
- ARE YOU SERIOUS?

21
00:00:53,250 --> 00:00:55,791
- SO YOU GUYS
ARE GONNA STAY HERE AND HELP ME?

22
00:00:55,875 --> 00:00:57,250
REALLY?

23
00:00:57,333 --> 00:00:59,291
JUST LIKE THE PRINCES
IN THE FAIRY TALE

24
00:00:59,375 --> 00:01:00,375
WHO BRAVELY FACE THEIR ENEMIES

25
00:01:00,458 --> 00:01:02,125
NO MATTER HOW FEROCIOUS
THEY MAY BE,

26
00:01:02,208 --> 00:01:04,750
AND FIGHT TO THE BITTER END
FOR THE PEOPLE THAT THEY LOVE,

27
00:01:04,833 --> 00:01:06,833
THESE TWO
ARE HERE TO PROTECT ME.

28
00:02:40,666 --> 00:02:43,416
( Nina whining )
I CAN'T BELIEVE MY MOM.

29
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,083
SHE RAN OFF
FOR A WEEKEND RETREAT

30
00:02:45,166 --> 00:02:46,916
AND THEN LEFT ME
TO DO ALL THE SHOPPING.

31
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,375
IT'S JUST NOT FAIR.

32
00:02:48,458 --> 00:02:52,208
EGGS, RICE, SOME MISO SOUP,
SOME SUGAR,

33
00:02:52,291 --> 00:02:55,666
WASABI, SOME... SUGAR.

34
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:57,041
( grunting )

35
00:02:57,125 --> 00:02:59,458
I CAN ALMOST REACH IT.

36
00:02:59,541 --> 00:03:01,500
JUST A LITTLE FURTHER.

37
00:03:01,583 --> 00:03:03,708
WHY DO THEY HAVE TO
MAKE THESE SHELVES SO TALL?

38
00:03:03,791 --> 00:03:06,625
I WISH I WERE TALLER.

39
00:03:06,708 --> 00:03:09,333
- NEED THIS?

40
00:03:09,416 --> 00:03:12,000
- YEAH, THANK YOU.

41
00:03:12,083 --> 00:03:15,291
- WHAT ELSE?
- UM, WELL...

42
00:03:15,375 --> 00:03:18,833
ZERO!  THERE'S NO WAY I'M GONNA
BUY ALL THAT JUNK FOOD.

43
00:03:18,916 --> 00:03:21,000
- DON'T BE SO STINGY.
- WHAT?

44
00:03:21,083 --> 00:03:22,875
YOU CAN'T POSSIBLY
EAT IT ALL ANYWAY,

45
00:03:22,958 --> 00:03:24,958
SO JUST STOP, UNLESS YOU'RE
GONNA BUY IT YOURSELF.

46
00:03:25,041 --> 00:03:26,875
DO I MAKE MYSELF CLEAR?

47
00:03:26,958 --> 00:03:29,916
- Man: LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
THANK YOU FOR YOUR PATIENCE.

48
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,208
I'M PLEASED TO ANNOUNCE

49
00:03:31,291 --> 00:03:33,083
THAT OUR ONE-TIME-ONLY SALE
BEGINS RIGHT NOW.

50
00:03:33,166 --> 00:03:34,833
HERE'S THE DEAL--
STUFF THIS BAG

51
00:03:34,916 --> 00:03:36,875
WITH AS MUCH MERCHANDISE
AS YOU CAN

52
00:03:36,958 --> 00:03:39,916
AND IT'LL ONLY COST YOU $3.
- ( all shouting )

53
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,708
- AMAZING.

54
00:03:41,791 --> 00:03:45,083
THIS STORE WAS ALL BUT EMPTY
UNTIL HE MADE HIS ANNOUNCEMENT.

55
00:03:45,166 --> 00:03:48,125
- MUST BE MAGIC.
- SO YOU GUYS READY TO GO?

56
00:03:48,208 --> 00:03:51,125
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU BOUGHT ALL THAT, ZERO.

57
00:03:51,208 --> 00:03:53,250
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU CAN EAT THAT MUCH?

58
00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:54,041
- OF COURSE.

59
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:55,333
- WELL, THANKS TO YOU,

60
00:03:55,416 --> 00:03:57,208
WE HAVE THESE COUPONS FOR
THE SHOPPING ARCADE.

61
00:03:57,291 --> 00:03:59,458
LET'S ENTER THE RAFFLE
ON THE WAY HOME.

62
00:03:59,541 --> 00:04:03,125
OH, WOW! THE FIRST PRIZE IS A
DELUXE TRIP TO THE HOT SPRINGS.

63
00:04:03,208 --> 00:04:05,416
- SWEET!  LET'S GO
PICK UP THE SPA PACKAGE.

64
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:07,083
- YOU DON'T PICK IT UP.

65
00:04:07,166 --> 00:04:09,458
YOU ENTER THE RAFFLE
FOR A CHANCE TO WIN THE PRIZE,

66
00:04:09,541 --> 00:04:11,083
SO DON'T GET YOUR HOPES UP.

67
00:04:11,166 --> 00:04:13,458
THE CHANCES OF US
ACTUALLY GOING ARE SLIM TO NONE.

68
00:04:13,541 --> 00:04:15,708
WE'LL BE LUCKY
TO EVEN GET THIRD PLACE.

69
00:04:17,666 --> 00:04:19,208
- WE HAVE A WINNER!

70
00:04:19,291 --> 00:04:22,041
THE FIRST-PLACE PRIZE
HAS BEEN TAKEN.

71
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:23,916
YOU'VE WON A FREE TRIP
FOR THREE

72
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,500
TO HARUYAMA HOT SPRINGS!

73
00:04:26,583 --> 00:04:27,833
- WHAT DID YOU SAY?

74
00:04:33,958 --> 00:04:36,291
WHY'D I HAVE TO WIN
THIS SPA GETAWAY

75
00:04:36,375 --> 00:04:39,916
ON THE WEEKEND WHEN BOTH
MY PARENTS ARE OUT OF TOWN?

76
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,583
MAYBE I COULD
JUST GO TO THE SPA ALONE.

77
00:04:42,666 --> 00:04:44,250
- Zero: NINA.
- HUH?

78
00:04:44,333 --> 00:04:46,500
- TA-DA!

79
00:04:46,583 --> 00:04:49,625
- UM, YEAH.
WHAT ARE YOU TWO DOING?

80
00:04:49,708 --> 00:04:51,500
- ( both laughing )

81
00:04:51,583 --> 00:04:53,583
- WE'RE PACKED AND READY
TO GO TO THE HOT SPRINGS!

82
00:04:53,666 --> 00:04:55,541
DOI!
- WHAT?

83
00:04:55,625 --> 00:04:57,833
- IT'LL BE FUN, NINA.
PROMISE.

84
00:04:57,916 --> 00:04:59,583
- WHAT?!

85
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:01,625
YOU WANT ME TO GO TO THE
HOT SPRINGS WITH YOU GUYS?

86
00:05:01,708 --> 00:05:03,833
- I WANNA GO TOO! I WANNA
GO TOO. I WANNA GO TOO.

87
00:05:03,916 --> 00:05:06,083
- AND WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THAT YOU'RE GONNA GO?

88
00:05:06,166 --> 00:05:07,625
- THIS ISN'T FAIR.

89
00:05:07,708 --> 00:05:09,291
I DON'T WANNA BE LEFT HOME ALONE
ALL WEEKEND

90
00:05:09,375 --> 00:05:10,791
WHILE YOU'RE OFF
HAVING FUN, ZURA.

91
00:05:10,875 --> 00:05:12,291
I CAN SNEAK
INTO THE HOT SPRINGS WITH YOU.

92
00:05:12,375 --> 00:05:13,833
NO ONE WILL EVEN KNOW I'M THERE,
I PROMISE.

93
00:05:13,916 --> 00:05:17,333
- SO WE'RE ALL GOING
TO THE HOT SPRINGS?

94
00:05:17,416 --> 00:05:20,375
WOW!
IT'S AWESOME.

95
00:05:20,458 --> 00:05:21,583
- AMAZING.

96
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:23,458
JUST LOOK AT THIS PLACE,
YOU GUYS.

97
00:05:23,541 --> 00:05:25,458
- I WONDER
WHAT KIND OF FOOD THEY'VE GOT.

98
00:05:25,541 --> 00:05:27,958
- I JUST WANNA TAKE
A NICE, RELAXING BUBBLE BATH.

99
00:05:28,041 --> 00:05:31,458
- ( thinking ) THIS HAS DISASTER
WRITTEN ALL OVER IT.

100
00:05:31,541 --> 00:05:33,833
( sighs )

101
00:05:33,916 --> 00:05:37,125
- OH, I DON'T BELIEVE THIS!

102
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:40,250
THAT GIRL IS DOING EVERYTHING
SHE CAN TO STEAL MY ICHII AWAY.

103
00:05:40,333 --> 00:05:42,958
I BET SHE HAS ALL SORTS OF STUFF
PLANNED FOR HIM TOO.

104
00:05:43,041 --> 00:05:45,208
WELL, I WON'T STAND
IDLY BY AND WATCH

105
00:05:45,291 --> 00:05:47,541
THAT TREACHEROUS LITTLE
VIXEN TAKE MY MAN FROM ME!

106
00:05:47,625 --> 00:05:50,041
I HOPE SHE KNOWS
SHE BROUGHT THIS ON HERSELF.

107
00:05:50,125 --> 00:05:51,208
GUESS I'LL JUST HAVE TO
USE

108
00:05:51,291 --> 00:05:53,083
MY SUPER SEXY
BOMB-DIDDLY-ICIOUS BODY

109
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:56,416
TO BRING MY SWEET LOVE BACK.
- PLEASE REFRAIN, ROKKA,

110
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:59,500
FROM ANY LEWD BEHAVIOR
WHILE WE'RE IN PUBLIC.

111
00:05:59,583 --> 00:06:01,250
- IT'S TIME TO CHECK IN.

112
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:07,166
- THIS ISN'T GOOD.
- ( rustling )

113
00:06:15,541 --> 00:06:18,041
- GUESS I'M HEARING THINGS.

114
00:06:28,208 --> 00:06:30,333
- I DON'T GET IT!
WE MADE A POINT TO CHECK IN

115
00:06:30,416 --> 00:06:33,541
WITH ICHII POSING AS MY OLDER
BROTHER AND ZERO AS MY COUSIN.

116
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:36,208
SO WHY DID THEY PUT US ALL
IN THE SAME ROOM TOGETHER?

117
00:06:36,291 --> 00:06:38,625
- WELL, ANYBODY WANT
TO CHECK OUT THE BATHS WITH ME?

118
00:06:38,708 --> 00:06:40,666
- I DO!
- ( both humming )

119
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:46,291
- WHAT'S WRONG?
- WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

120
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:48,291
WHY DON'T YOU GO
INTO THE BATHROOM TO CHANGE?

121
00:06:48,375 --> 00:06:49,625
- MAYBE YOU
SHOULD STOP LOOKING

122
00:06:49,708 --> 00:06:51,250
AND GET CHANGED YOURSELF,
NINA.

123
00:06:51,333 --> 00:06:52,666
- YOU TWO GO ON AHEAD.

124
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:54,875
I'LL MEET UP WITH YOU LATER.
ENJOY.

125
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:59,416
- Both: HUH?

126
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:02,000
- I CANNOT BELIEVE

127
00:07:02,083 --> 00:07:04,625
WHAT I JUST SAW.

128
00:07:04,708 --> 00:07:07,125
- ( both laughing )

129
00:07:07,208 --> 00:07:08,833
- WAIT.

130
00:07:08,916 --> 00:07:13,208
I JUST NEED TO CALM DOWN
AND STOP GETTING SO EXCITED.

131
00:07:13,291 --> 00:07:16,166
- Gou: I HAVE SOMETHING EVEN
MORE EXCITING IN STORE FOR YOU.

132
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:19,416
- AREN'T YOU--
- THAT'S RIGHT.

133
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:23,083
- UM...
- I'M ROKKA'S BUTLER, GOU.

134
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:25,875
AND I'M AFRAID
YOU MADE A BIG MISTAKE

135
00:07:25,958 --> 00:07:29,166
COMING OUT HERE TONIGHT WITHOUT
ZERO AND ICHII BY YOUR SIDE.

136
00:07:29,250 --> 00:07:32,583
SO I'LL SEIZE THIS GOLDEN
OPPORTUNITY AND TAKE YOU AWAY.

137
00:07:32,666 --> 00:07:35,041
AND THOSE TWO WILL NEVER
BE ABLE TO FIND YOU AGAIN.

138
00:07:35,125 --> 00:07:37,791
SUMMONING PHANTOM MAGIC.

139
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:39,833
AND NOW, GAME SQUARE.

140
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:46,166
- AH!

141
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:49,041
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?!

142
00:07:49,125 --> 00:07:52,083
AHH! ARE THOSE
WHAT I THINK THEY ARE?

143
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:53,666
- THAT'S RIGHT, NINA.

144
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:56,791
I'VE TRANSPORTED YOU
INTO A PINBALL MACHINE

145
00:07:56,875 --> 00:07:58,708
IN THE HOT SPRINGS ARCADE.

146
00:07:58,791 --> 00:08:02,333
- HEY, GET ME OUT OF THIS THING
RIGHT NOW, DO YOU HEAR ME?!

147
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:05,250
- STOP COMPLAINING OR I'LL MAKE
THIS MUCH WORSE FOR YOU.

148
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:08,125
- OH, YEAH?
I'D LIKE TO SEE YOU TRY IT.

149
00:08:08,208 --> 00:08:10,250
- ALL RIGHT. LET'S GET
ON WITH THE GAME THEN.

150
00:08:10,333 --> 00:08:12,166
IT'S SURE TO BE A BLAST.

151
00:08:14,083 --> 00:08:15,666
GOOD LUCK NOW, NINA.

152
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:21,083
- ( thinking ) WHAT'S THAT?
WHAT IS THAT NOISE?

153
00:08:26,125 --> 00:08:28,458
- DON'T LET YOUR GUARD DOWN
JUST YET.

154
00:08:30,125 --> 00:08:32,291
- OH, NO!

155
00:08:34,291 --> 00:08:35,666
AHH!

156
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:38,333
- LADY ROKKA IS PRETTY
UPSET WITH YOU.

157
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:45,333
PERHAPS
THIS WILL CALM HER NERVES.

158
00:08:45,416 --> 00:08:47,416
- HELP ME!

159
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:50,458
- THAT'S IT!
I WON'T LET YOU DO THAT.

160
00:08:55,125 --> 00:08:57,583
MAGICAL BREAK!

161
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:11,458
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
- I ALMOST HAD THE PEARL.

162
00:09:11,541 --> 00:09:13,958
- NO WAY!  YOU'RE NEVER
GONNA GET THE PEARL.

163
00:09:14,041 --> 00:09:16,083
NOT AS LONG
AS I'M PROTECTING NINA.

164
00:09:16,166 --> 00:09:18,375
- NINA!  ZERO!

165
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:21,625
IT'S YOU.
- ESCAPE HOLE.

166
00:09:21,708 --> 00:09:24,750
- HEY, STOP!
WAIT.

167
00:09:26,625 --> 00:09:30,333
HE GOT AWAY.
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

168
00:09:30,416 --> 00:09:32,666
- YEAH.
AND THANKS FOR ASKING, ICHII.

169
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,916
- IF GOU CAME ALL THE WAY
OUT HERE TO ATTACK NINA,

170
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,250
THERE MAY BE OTHERS.
WE CAN'T LET OUR GUARD DOWN.

171
00:09:37,333 --> 00:09:39,291
- I KNOW.
- ( women shouting )

172
00:09:39,375 --> 00:09:43,291
- OH MY!
LOOK AT THE MESS YOU MADE.

173
00:09:43,375 --> 00:09:45,416
- SORRY ABOUT THAT.

174
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:47,583
I THOUGHT THE PINBALL MACHINE
COULD SUPPORT MY WEIGHT,

175
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:49,208
BUT I GUESS I WAS WRONG

176
00:09:49,291 --> 00:09:51,666
'CAUSE IT BROKE
WHEN I STOOD ON IT.  MY BAD.

177
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:53,833
- SOMEONE STOP THEM.

178
00:09:53,916 --> 00:09:55,458
- All: WE'LL BE GOING NOW.

179
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,958
- ( owl hooting )

180
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:01,750
- HA-HA!
ZURA, ZURA, ZURA.

181
00:10:01,833 --> 00:10:03,875
- ARGH! ZERO.

182
00:10:03,958 --> 00:10:06,041
WHY'D YOU HAVE TO GO
AND BREAK THE MACHINE?

183
00:10:06,125 --> 00:10:08,208
- I DID WHAT I HAD TO DO
IN ORDER TO SAVE YOU,

184
00:10:08,291 --> 00:10:09,375
SO STOP COMPLAINING.

185
00:10:09,458 --> 00:10:11,125
- BUT STILL!
- THERE'S NO NEED

186
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:12,875
TO KEEP ARGUING ABOUT IT,
YOU TWO.

187
00:10:12,958 --> 00:10:14,666
- LOOK, ZERO--

188
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:17,000
- I HAD NO CHOICE
BUT THE BREAK THE MACHINE, NINA.

189
00:10:17,083 --> 00:10:18,416
SO JUST DROP IT.

190
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,750
- Forte:
ARE YOU AN EXAMINEE TOO?

191
00:10:22,791 --> 00:10:25,250
- WHO ARE YOU?

192
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:28,500
- FORTE.
EXAMINEE NUMBER 004.

193
00:10:28,583 --> 00:10:31,500
- AND MY EXAMINEE NUMBER
IS 005.

194
00:10:31,583 --> 00:10:32,583
I'M GOU.

195
00:10:32,666 --> 00:10:34,041
- SORRY TO DAMPEN
YOUR SPIRITS, GOU,

196
00:10:34,125 --> 00:10:37,000
BUT THAT CRYSTAL PEARL
BELONGS TO US.

197
00:10:37,083 --> 00:10:39,250
AND HERE'S A WARNING FOR YOU.

198
00:10:39,333 --> 00:10:42,125
I'D ADVISE YOU NOT TO
TAKE NINA'S PROTECTORS LIGHTLY.

199
00:10:42,208 --> 00:10:44,375
ZERO AND ICHII
ARE BOTH FORMIDABLE OPPONENTS

200
00:10:44,458 --> 00:10:45,791
WITH POWERFUL
MAGIC ATTACKS,

201
00:10:45,875 --> 00:10:48,125
AND THEY'LL STOP AT NOTHING
TO KEEP HER SAFE.

202
00:10:48,208 --> 00:10:50,541
AND IF YOU ATTACK THEM
WITH A HALF-PLANNED OFFENSIVE,

203
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:54,041
THEN YOU'LL SURELY BE DEFEATED.
- THEN IN THAT CASE,

204
00:10:54,125 --> 00:10:56,041
I HAVE A WARNING FOR YOU
AS WELL.

205
00:10:58,416 --> 00:11:01,666
THE SUMMER KIMONO
THAT YOU'RE WEARING?

206
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:05,416
- YEAH?
WHAT ABOUT MY SUMMER KIMONO?

207
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:08,000
- YOU KNOW IT'S FOR WOMEN.

208
00:11:08,083 --> 00:11:10,625
- AH!

209
00:11:10,708 --> 00:11:13,833
SAN, THAT LITTLE BRAT!
SHE TRICKED ME!

210
00:11:13,916 --> 00:11:16,041
I KNEW THIS WAS FOR WOMEN!

211
00:11:16,125 --> 00:11:19,916
- SOMEHOW, THAT KID
MANAGES TO PULL IT OFF.

212
00:11:23,208 --> 00:11:24,750
- ZURA, ZURA, ZURA.

213
00:11:24,833 --> 00:11:26,875
- OKAY, WE'LL SEE YOU LATER,
NINA.

214
00:11:26,958 --> 00:11:29,416
- OKAY, BUT...

215
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:31,958
WHAT IF SOMEONE
TRIES TO ATTACK ME

216
00:11:32,041 --> 00:11:34,833
WHILE I'M ALONE IN THE BATH?

217
00:11:34,916 --> 00:11:37,041
- YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

218
00:11:37,125 --> 00:11:39,083
AS LONG AS YOU'VE GOT
THAT LOLLIPOP,

219
00:11:39,166 --> 00:11:42,166
NO ONE CAN LAY A HAND ON YOU.

220
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:45,208
- I GUESS I CAN RELAX NOW
KNOWING THAT THIS LOLLIPOP

221
00:11:45,291 --> 00:11:47,458
WILL PROTECT ME
FROM ANY ATTACKERS.

222
00:11:47,541 --> 00:11:49,750
