312
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,291
'CAUSE THERE ISN'T ANYTHING
TO SEE.

313
00:16:17,208 --> 00:16:19,333
- HE'S SUCH AN INSENSITIVE JERK.

314
00:16:19,416 --> 00:16:21,458
